parameters.name: DATE
parameters.description:
Time column. This field contains time in PDS format:                  
                        yydoy.

parameters.name: PERIAPSIS_TIME
parameters.description:
The time of the orbital periapsis given in the format HH:MM:SS where HH
                        is the 2 digit hour, MM in the 2 digit minute, and SS is the 2 digit   
                        second.

parameters.name: INBOUND_SECONDS
parameters.description:
The second-of-day of the inbound bowshock 
                        crossing.

parameters.name: INBOUND_TIME
parameters.description:
The time of the inbound bowshock crossing given in the format HH:MM:SS 
                        where HH is the 2 digit hour, MM in the 2 digit minute, and SS is the  
                        2 digit second.

parameters.name: INBOUND_LATITUDE
parameters.description:
The venusian latitude of the spacecraft at inbound bowshock crossing  
                        given in degrees.

parameters.name: INBOUND_LOCAL_SOLAR_TIME
parameters.description:
The local solar time of the spacecraft at inbound bowshock crossing   
                        given in hours.

parameters.name: INBOUND_ALTITUDE
parameters.description:
The altitude of the spacecraft at inbound bowshock crossing given in   
                        kilometers.

parameters.name: INBOUND_SOLAR_ZENITH_ANGLE
parameters.description:
The solar zenith angle of the spacecraft at the inbound bowshock       
                        crossing given in degrees.

parameters.name: OUTBOUND_SECONDS
parameters.description:
The second-of-day of the outbound bowshock 
                        crossing.

parameters.name: OUTBOUND_TIME
parameters.description:
The time of the outbound bowshock crossing given in the format HH:MM:SS
                        where HH is the 2 digit hour, MM in the 2 digit minute, and SS is the 2
                        digit second.

parameters.name: OUTBOUND_LATITUDE
parameters.description:
The venusian latitude of the spacecraft at outbound bowshock crossing  
                        given in degrees.

parameters.name: OUTBOUND_LOCAL_SOLAR_TIME
parameters.description:
The local solar time of the spacecraft at outbound bowshock crossing   
                        given in hours.

parameters.name: OUTBOUND_ALTITUDE
parameters.description:
The altitude of the spacecraft at outbound bowshock crossing given in  
                        kilometers.

parameters.name: OUTBOUND_SOLAR_ZENITH_ANGLE
parameters.description:
The solar zenith angle of the spacecraft at the outbound bowshock      
                        crossing given in degrees.
